WEBVTT

00:00.160 --> 00:01.280
After the Yiyang battle

00:01.480 --> 00:03.720
Zhao took my military command

00:04.000 --> 00:05.400
Drove my tribe out

00:06.000 --> 00:06.840
Now

00:07.000 --> 00:09.280
I can only lead my tribe wandering

00:09.280 --> 00:10.120
Begging to survive

00:10.240 --> 00:11.000
I know

00:11.960 --> 00:13.880
Your Highness wants to attack Nandu

00:14.240 --> 00:16.360
But troubled by Qingzhou Army's restraint

00:16.920 --> 00:18.440
I'm also a commander

00:19.160 --> 00:21.200
Naturally can see the current situation

00:22.160 --> 00:24.680
My tribe has many skilled fighters

00:25.200 --> 00:26.960
Only lacking weapons and food

00:27.200 --> 00:29.480
If Your Highness can give us two thousand sets of armor

00:29.480 --> 00:30.560
One thousand warhorses

00:30.680 --> 00:31.960
One hundred days of rations

00:32.880 --> 00:35.520
I will block Qingzhou Army for Your Highness
